419
00:27:19,704 --> 00:27:23,970
Thank you very much, ladies and gentlemen.
Have a great day. God bless.

420
00:27:44,896 --> 00:27:46,989
Yo, man. All right.

421
00:27:54,372 --> 00:27:58,809
<i>Now here in this flesh-colored world</i>

422
00:28:00,611 --> 00:28:05,776
<i>I am dreamin' about the impossible</i>

423
00:28:07,718 --> 00:28:12,417
<i>'Cause I know impossible things</i>

424
00:28:12,623 --> 00:28:16,389
<i>Happen every day</i>

425
00:28:20,565 --> 00:28:24,228
<i>And the difference between us</i>

426
00:28:24,869 --> 00:28:27,667
<i>Is fading away</i>

427
00:28:28,372 --> 00:28:31,705
<i>Like all of the small things</i>

428
00:28:31,809 --> 00:28:34,471
<i>That make up my day</i>

429
00:28:35,179 --> 00:28:38,046
<i>This world is my town</i>

430
00:28:38,249 --> 00:28:41,650
<i>I don't care what they say</i>

431
00:28:55,900 --> 00:28:57,128
Ira?

432
00:28:58,035 --> 00:28:59,093
Dad.

433
00:28:59,203 --> 00:29:01,637
- Thought you were going out of town.
- No, I put it off.

434
00:29:01,739 --> 00:29:03,832
I'm going over to Arnie's.
You wanna come with?

435
00:29:03,941 --> 00:29:07,206
I'm working. I don't know whether I should
order through the month...

436
00:29:07,311 --> 00:29:10,474
or just start pulling stuff
