437
00:29:12,583 --> 00:29:15,552
Remember that?
This room was filled with Knicks.

438
00:29:15,653 --> 00:29:17,780
What was I like? Five, six?

439
00:29:19,724 --> 00:29:22,557
No basketball stars
coming in here these days.

440
00:29:22,660 --> 00:29:24,651
These days you wouldn't want them in here.

441
