You sure we're doing
the right thing here, Dad?

446
00:29:42,847 --> 00:29:45,145
- What do you mean?
- I don't know.

447
00:29:45,783 --> 00:29:47,774
I wish we could hold on a little longer.

448
00:29:47,885 --> 00:29:50,012
This restaurant means a lot
to a lot of people.

449
00:29:50,121 --> 00:29:54,455
- Ira, please, don't be so damn sentimental.
- I'm not being sentimental.

450
00:29:55,426 --> 00:29:58,190
- I just care, okay?
- Ira, don't be stupid.

451
00:29:58,296 --> 00:30:01,288
You think a deal like this
is gonna last forever?

452
00:30:01,399 --> 00:30:02,991
We do this now...

453
00:30:03,801 --> 00:30:05,894
and we can take care of a lot of people.

454
00:30:06,003 --> 00:30:08,528
We draw this out
and everyone's gonna end up screwed.

455
00:30:08,639 --> 00:30:10,800
- Yeah, but...
- But nothing.

456
00:30:11,709 --> 00:30:14,473
Don't be such a worrywart. Lighten up.

457
00:30:15,313 --> 00:30:18,180
See you worry, you eat.
That's what happens.

458
00:30:18,382 --> 00:30:20,680
And I can tell
you've been worrying a lot lately...

459
00:30:20,785 --> 00:30:23,948
because you got a little jellyroll
happening here.

460
00:30:25,022 --> 00:30:28,355
- Dad, no matter what I do, you got to...
- What?

461
00:30:31,796 --> 00:30:33,093
Forget it.

462
00:30:38,002 --> 00:30:40,869
I'm going over to Arnie's.
You wanna come with or not?

