"Well, I'm up here still

1114
01:19:48,513 --> 01:19:50,913
"And ready to jump, no fear

1115
01:19:51,016 --> 01:19:54,076
"I'll go it all alone
I'll make it happen on my own

1116
01:19:54,186 --> 01:19:55,585
"I will rise

1117
01:19:55,821 --> 01:19:58,085
"I will rise, I will rise

1118
01:19:58,290 --> 01:19:59,814
"And you will see

1119
01:19:59,925 --> 01:20:01,085
"Look up

1120
01:20:01,426 --> 01:20:03,792
"Look up here at me"

