01:21:05,257 --> 01:21:07,282
Glenmorangie, please. Double, up.

1122
01:21:07,826 --> 01:21:10,954
- Dewars okay?
- Dewars is fine.

1123
01:21:11,396 --> 01:21:13,296
- Dewars will do the trick.
- Right.

1124
01:21:13,799 --> 01:21:16,529
You going for the serious stuff, honey.

1125
01:21:17,702 --> 01:21:19,602
I've had a serious day.

1126
01:21:20,005 --> 01:21:23,270
- Let your hair down.
- I wish I had hair to let down.

1127
01:21:24,743 --> 01:21:26,404
So you can laugh.

1128
01:21:26,878 --> 01:21:28,106
I try.

1129
01:21:29,815 --> 01:21:31,510
Here's to trying.

1130
01:21:33,451 --> 01:21:34,713
Honey...

1131
01:21:35,453 --> 01:21:37,512
you had a little trouble tonight?

1132
01:21:38,123 --> 01:21:39,215
Yeah.

1133
01:21:39,324 --> 01:21:43,055
A little encounter
with some of our endangered black youth.

1134
01:21:43,361 --> 01:21:45,090
If only I'd been wearing my ribbon.

1135
01:21:45,197 --> 01:21:46,630
What's that?

1136
01:21:47,399 --> 01:21:49,526
Nothing, it's a bad joke.

1137
01:21:50,235 --> 01:21:51,497
Cheers.

1138
01:21:57,108 --> 01:21:58,632
Friday night.

1139
01:22:02,347 --> 01:22:04,872
- This place is gonna close, you know.
- Say what?

1140
01:22:04,983 --> 01:22:06,211
This place.

1141
01:22:06,318 --> 01:22:09,219
