Become a high-rise.

1142
01:22:09,321 --> 01:22:11,585
This whole neighborhood, actually.

1143
01:22:11,690 --> 01:22:14,625
Where did you get
this information from, honey?

1144
01:22:15,827 --> 01:22:17,818
I'm the man responsible.

1145
01:22:18,897 --> 01:22:20,694
Ain't that something.

1146
01:22:21,366 --> 01:22:22,765
It is.

1147
01:22:23,935 --> 01:22:25,630
You're the man.

1148
01:22:26,371 --> 01:22:28,305
I am the man, yes.

1149
01:22:29,541 --> 01:22:32,009
This afternoon, I wasn't the man...

1150
01:22:32,110 --> 01:22:35,011
but I'm gonna try and see if I can't fix that.

1151
01:22:35,146 --> 01:22:37,671
