selling the property out from under us.

1156
01:22:56,167 --> 01:22:57,759
What do you mean "us"?

1157
01:22:58,003 --> 01:23:00,198
The owners of this place aren't black.

1158
01:23:00,305 --> 01:23:02,034
They may as well be.

1159
01:23:02,407 --> 01:23:05,399
