1160
01:23:05,911 --> 01:23:09,779
- You wanna make everything the same?
- It's not gonna change that much.

1161
01:23:09,881 --> 01:23:12,873
It'll still have the same flavor...

1162
01:23:13,051 --> 01:23:15,042
just cleaner. Safer.

1163
01:23:15,453 --> 01:23:19,321
Honey, you can't wash out
all the color and keep the flavor.

1164
01:23:21,693 --> 01:23:22,853
Jesus.

1165
01:23:25,430 --> 01:23:28,331
I didn't come in here to take on the world.

1166
01:23:30,635 --> 01:23:32,535
Here's to your success.

1167
01:23:32,804 --> 01:23:34,772
Maybe yours will be mine.

1168
01:23:36,641 --> 01:23:38,074
Thank you.

1169
01:23:39,311 --> 01:23:41,074
That would be nice.

1170
01:23:46,584 --> 01:23:47,846
Hit me.

1171
01:23:49,621 --> 01:23:51,486
You're the man all right.

1172
01:23:52,757 --> 01:23:55,988
- Nice to know you.
- Nice to know you, too.

1173
01:24:01,299 --> 01:24:03,529
So where you going from here?

1174
01:24:04,936 --> 01:24:06,563
You mean tonight?

1175
01:24:09,441 --> 01:24:11,500
I haven't thought that far.

1176
01:24:13,044 --> 01:24:14,534
You got time.

1177
01:24:15,046 --> 01:24:16,536
Think about it.

1178
01:24:17,682 --> 01:24:18,808
Okay.

1179
01:24:22,520 --> 01:24:24,351
The music is good.

1180
01:24:26,858 --> 01:24:28,086
Classic.

1181
01:24:32,063 --> 01:24:34,258
My world is changing.

1182
01:25:19,878 --> 01:25:22,108
<i>What's happening?</i>

1183
01:25:22,714 --> 01:25:25,148
<i>Nice night in Brooklyn.</i>
